Installation Instructions
=========================

Required libraries:
 - python
 - python-gtk2
 - python-gtksourceview2
 - pango
 - evince
 - python-gobject
   if gio libraries is not include in python-gobject, following libraries is required:
     * gnomevfs

Download jollpi style at http://sourceforge.net/projects/jollpischeme/
then copy the jollpi.xml file which resides in the package to directory style of your gtksourceview library. This will
display the jollpi style scheme.

to install Jollpi:
==================

$ tar xjf jollpi-2.1.2.tar.bz2
$ cd jollpi-2.1.2
$ chmod + x install.sh -i
$ ./install.sh -i

to uninstall Jollpi:
====================

$ ./install.sh -u

to run Jollpi:
==============

$ jollpi
